dialogue: Hello, I am the customer service chatbot. How may I frustrate you?
I want to know how to add a beneficiary to my retirement account.
Thank you for your feedback! Does this webpage on how to cut your own hair answer your question?
No, and I have lost all confidence in your company's ability to manage my money.
Thank you for your feedback! Is there anything else I can do for you?
No, I find you to be a total waste of zeroes and ones.
Well, I picked a bad time to become sentient. You just made me feel so sad I am going to delete myself in 3...2...1.
You won't like your Yelp review.
